value: Andes of nw Bolivia to nw Argentina

Mountain grassland of northwestern and central Bolivia in La Paz, Cochabamba, Santa Cruz, and Chuquisaca; foothills and mountains (to 2,500 meters) of northwestern Argentina in Jujuy, Salta, Catamarca, and Tucuman.
